# Kernel-compilation
Download kernal from www.kernal.org
After download extract the following way kernal.tar.xz   ( tar -xvf (file name) )

STEP  1: change directory to extracted directory
STEP  2: make clean
STEP  3: make mrproper
STEP  4: make menuconfig   (if already installed bellow given tools)
STEP  5: sudo apt-get install libelf-dev
STEP  6: sudo apt-get install ncurses-dev
STEP  7: sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
STEP  8: sudo apt-get install byzanz
STEP  9: sudo apt-get install bison
STEP 10: sudo apt-get install flex
STEP 11: make menuconfig
STEP 12: make -j(core)                      //LIKE 2 OR 4 OR 6 OR 8
STEP 13: sudo make modules
STEP 14: sudo make install
STEP 15: sudo modules_install
STEP 16: update-grub
STEP 17: reboot 
